[[File:Wiki-gokkun.png|thumb|An artist's impression of a woman drinking semen]] {{Nihongo|'''Gokkun'''|ゴックン}} is a [[Japanese language|Japanese]] term for sexual activity in which a person consumes the [[semen]] of one or more men, usually from some kind of container.<ref name="dufour">{{cite book|title=La cité perverse: libéralisme et pornographie|series=Bibliothèque Médiations|first=Dany-Robert|last=Dufour|publisher=[[Éditions Denoël]]|year=2009|isbn=2-207-26120-4 |page=12|url=https://books.google.com/books?ei=xnvZTOeeN4qVOpmKlf8I }}</ref> Commonly used containers include cups, large [[beaker (glassware)|beaker]]s, bowls, baking pans, and wine or cocktail glasses. Most of these scenarios involve the semen of multiple men.
"Gokkun" can also refer to the sexual act of swallowing semen after performing [[fellatio]] or participating in a [[bukkake]].<ref name="dufour"/><ref>{{Cite book|title=Extremes: contradictions in contemporary Japan|first=G. M.|last=Thomas|publisher=Kaichan|year=2004|isbn=0-9546789-0-7|page=177}}</ref> The word "gokkun" is onomatopoetic, and translates roughly as the English word "gulp", the sound made by swallowing.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seekjapan.jp/article-1/744/The+(Almost)+Complete+Japanzine+Dictionary+of+Japan+Sex |title=The (Almost) Complete Japanzine Dictionary of Japan Sex |publisher=Seekjapan |last=Wilks |first=J |accessdate=2010-05-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100202033818/http://www.seekjapan.jp/article-1/744/The%2B%28Almost%29%2BComplete%2BJapanzine%2BDictionary%2Bof%2BJapan%2BSex |archivedate=February 2, 2010 |df= }}</ref>
